<br>
As for weapons, I have no idea about slashers. Go for crafted perhaps? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#ffffff><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/blighttanksofdaoc.showUserPublicProfile?gid=vallyn@lighttanksofdaoc>Vallyn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Journeyman</span><br>  Posts: 11<br> <font color=#000000>(5/12/03 6:47 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm9.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=55.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Keltoi</span><hr size=1> The keltoi chain armor is Duskwalker and is decent for melee, but i'm not sure how it compares with the Teapok drops (Teapok wasn't itemized when i lvled throu there). As for swords Dark Short Swords drop in Keltoi, and i believe they are very similiar to the bloody short swords just a couple lvls higher. Keltoi also has decent drops for misc items. Anyway there is my 2c worth.<br>
