<br>
What's weird about *all* the Tepok armor sets is that they seem to focus on resists more than any other lowbie armor.<br>
<br>
I am betting that the drops they are planning on boosting are the super-crappy ones that the named mobs drop.  For example, Overseer Tepok himself drops a Tattered Robe of the Overseer that is 70% quality!  It's no wonder that few folks ever go to Tepok, except for the occasional epic quest. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/blighttanksofdaoc.showUserPublicProfile?gid=erithralmon>Erithralmon</A> at: 5/13/03 6:55:00 pm<br></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm9.showPrevMessage?topicID=55.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm9.showNextMessage?topicID=55.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm9.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=55.topic&index=3><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm9.emailToFriend?topicID=55.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm9.threadControl?topicID=55.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/slate/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm9.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=55.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm9.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=55.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscr